quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  98,8,"Omurungo kwabu ewa Nyasaye wabu Omulesi ni emikunda chilaliwa tawe, echiburangamwo emialo. Ako nikhu ulia uritsanga Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi."
  99,1,"Olwa liloba liliseswa okhuseswa khwalio!"
  99,2,"Ne olwa liloba liliyinia emisiko chialio!"
  99,3,"Ne Omundu aliboola mbu, "Libeele lirie?”"
  99,4,"Inyanga eyo liliboola amakhuwa kalio."
  99,5,"Khulwa okhuba Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi alifimbulile!"
  99,6,"Inyanga eyo Abandu balirula nibakabukhane emikanda khobalolesibwe ebikhole biabu!"
  99,7,"Kho ulia ukhola amalayi shinga obusiro bwoluloolo, yakhakalole!"
  99,8,"Ne ulia ukhola amabii shinga obusiro bwoluloolo, yakhakalole!"
  100,1,"Nditsuba khutsifarasi tsitsitsaanga tsimbilo nitsiyesaana."
  100,2,"Nitsirusia tsinzesele tsiomulilo khukhupa ebilekeyi biatsio hasi."
  100,3,"Nende etsiseeranga liye itsuli."
  100,4,"Ne eno nitsitumuula olufu."
  100,5,"Mana tsyule hakari womukanda (kwa abasuku)."
  100,6,"Toto Omundu ni omukhayi muno wa (tsimbabaasi tsia) Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi."
  100,7,"Ne toto ye mwene ni omuloli muno khu elo!"
  100,8,"Ne toto ye ali neshinani muno shiokhuyanza omwandu!"
  100,9,"Kho koo shamanyilekho olwa ebili mubilindwa bilipukululwa tawe?"